			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Orin has abductee Laezel, and is impersonating Laezel. Orin-as-Laezel has also taken Yenna hostage pretending to the players that Yenna is in fact Orin-in-disguise.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;During that camp-night confrontation, bad skill rolls or if players encouraged Orin-as-Laezel to kill Yenna, Yenna would be killed.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;This is the SwD for this encounter on Yenna's body to get a little more information about what really happened." />
